name: dwellkart
overview:
ABOUT US

Dwellkart.com serves an essential human need - to look beautiful. We offer only the best so you can remain assured of the quality of every item we sell. We aim to provide you an incredible shopping experience, a wide range of AD jewellery and excellent customer service.

Quality Assurance

Every product we sell is 100% genuine. Customer Delight We strive to delight customers with our service and will go the extra mile to keep them happy. Apart from maintaining high standards of quality.

Dwellkart going to live in 2012 with the objective of making AD Jewellery easily available to anyone who had internet access.

Our services like Cash on Delivery, a 30-day replacement policy, free shipping - and of course the great prices that we offer. Then there’s our dedicated Dwellkart delivery team that works round the clock to personally make sure packages reach on time. And it’s all thanks to you
